The largest residence types.  These require a large plot of land.  
They start with ten rooms, but have no maximum number of rooms.  They 
require 4 million gold, the price of the land, and can only be built 
by players of level 19+75 and above. 

Palaces come with the color-code converter upgrade automatically.  
With future housing storage limits being based on size (number of 
rooms) for a given house, these will be by far the most desirable, as 
well as the most costly and difficult to attain. 

